data.description: Oak Island Oasis ! 4-Car Garage on 1.5 Lot is a Rare Find on Oak Island ! This open concept home has all of your living on the primary floor, a terrific screened-in porch and a firepit area ready for cool Fall nights under the Stars of Oak Island Heaven ! This 3 Bedroom-2 Bath home features granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, gorgeous cabinetry, and deluxe pull-outs in the kitchen drawers. The Master has a 'His' and 'Hers' closet and a glass walk-in shower. From the 4-CAR GARAGE....you will walk into the laundry area which includes the washer/dryer. Most of the appliances are GE. You will walk through the kitchen to the dining area and out to the screen porch where you will see the fenced in backyard with a double door gate to allow room to back in your boat, your trailer, your small RV or any other large outdoor equipment and toys ! PLUS, you will see a 'cute-as-pie' shed in the backyard for plenty of storage or to be converted into a 'SheShed' or the 'DawgHouse' at your whimsey ! Agent was informed that the home was originally built by SouthernHome Builders and wired for 220 volts to accommodate a hottub if desired, and also wired for a 50 amp box to plug in a generator if needed (located outside rear garage door).  Buyer will need to confirm this amp information during their Due Diligence. An Outdoor Shower is included for rinsing off the sand of the day! Oak Island is only 15 min from the galleries, restaurants and antique shops of Historic Downtown Southport. Centrally located between the airports of N.Mrytle Beach SC and Wilmington NC. This home is NOT in a flood zone and will not require flood insurance. Public Beach Accesses run the length of Oak Island with ''walk-overs'' on SE 9th Street and SE 20th Street. Golf Carts are allowed on Oak Island, please check with the town ordinances for golf cart requirements. The closest beach accesses from this home would be Middleton or SE 40th St. Call Us For A Showing Today
